description: This Chainlink VRF hall of fame Yulenka purrs with a rating of 96, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 96, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 8 for North, 3 for East, 2 for South, and 2 for West. Yulenka has the personality suit of yenta. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/80961-83224-0.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Yulenka [96 Votes, Hall of Fame]
